com.ahok.cuber.controller

Class DriverController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ahok.cuber.controller.DriverController

  • @RestController
public class DriverController
extends java.lang.Object
    Rest CRUD Driver Controller

    Available endpoints:

    • GET drivers/all Get a list of all Drivers
    • GET drivers/get/{id} Get Driver by id
    • POST drivers/add Add new Driver
    • PUT drivers/update Update Driver
    • DELETE drivers/delete/{id} Delete Driver
